summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 14106 entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of Westlake Avenue from Denny Way to Mercer Street, all in the City of Seattle by grading and re-grading the same to the elevations herein below set forth and by constructing all necessary slopes or retaining walls for cuts or fills upon the real property abutting upon said streets and avenues, and by reconstructing sewers where necessary, all in accordance with Resolution No. 144, of the City Council of the City of Seattle.
